quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,Ni (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe
  55,2,Yigishije (umuntu) Qur’an
  55,3,Yaremye umuntu
  55,4,Amwigisha ububonezamvugo
  55,5,Izuba n’ukwezi bigendera ku mubare (no kuri gahunda ya Allah)
  55,6,"N’ibimera birandaranda ndetse n’ibiti, byose birubama (bikicisha bugufi imbere ya Allah)"
  55,7,N’ikirere yagishyize hejuru cyane (y’isi) ndetse ashyiraho n’ibipimo (bya buri kintu)
  55,8,Kugira ngo mutarengera ibipimo (byagenwe)
  55,9,"Bityo, mujye mupima ibintu byose mukoresheje ubutabera, kandi ntimukagabanye ibipimo"
  55,10,N’isi (Allah) yayishyiriyeho ibiremwa
  55,11,Iriho imbuto n’imitende ifite imbuto zitwikiriwe n’ibishishwa
  55,12,Ndetse n’impeke (z’ubwoko bunyuranye); iz’inyamisogwe n’izihumura
  55,13,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,14,(Allah) yaremye umuntu (Adamu) mu itaka ryumye ukomangaho rikirangira nk’ibikoresho bibumbye mu ibumba
  55,15,Anarema amajini mu birimi by’umuriro
  55,16,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,17,(Ni we) Nyagasani w’Uburasirazuba bubiri akaba na Nyagasani w’Uburengerazuba bubiri
  55,18,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,19,Yahuje inyanja ebyiri (ifite amazi y’urubogobogo n’indi y’urwunyunyu)
  55,20,"Hagati yazo ahashyira urubibi (ruzitandukanya), zikinjiranamo ariko ntizivange"
  55,21,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,22,Muri zo havamo amasaro arabagirana (Lu-ulu-u) na Marijani
  55,23,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,24,"Kandi (Allah ni we) ufite ububasha ku mato manini agendera mu nyanja, ameze nk’imisozi"
  55,25,Nonese (yemwe bantu na mwe majini) ni izihe ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana